org.onexus.collection.api

Interface IEntitySet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, Iterable<IEntity>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyEntitySet, TsvEntitySet

    public interface IEntitySet
extends IEntity, Iterable<IEntity>

    A set of IEntity.

    This class extends IEntity class because it follows the Cursor pattern. On each next() call the instance of the IEntitySet points to the next entity.

    Author:
    Jordi Deu-Pons
